BEGIN:VCALENDAR
VERSION:2.0
PRODID:-//notapattern//calendar export 1.0//EN
CALSCALE:GREGORIAN
METHOD:PUBLISH
X-WR-CALNAME:Beaches\, A New Musical
X-WR-TIMEZONE:America/New_York
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Beaches\, A New Musical
DTSTART:20260327T233000Z
DTEND:20260328T015000Z
DTSTAMP:20260326T185310Z
UID:987189
DESCRIPTION:<p><em>Beaches\, A New Musical</em>\, based on the best-sellin
 g novel that became the blockbuster film\, brings to the stage one of the 
 most iconic friendships in popular culture. This sweeping\, emotional\, an
 d joy-filled new musical follows the vivacious Cee Cee and elegant Bertie\
 , who meet as children and become fast friends. From pen-pals to roommates
  to romantic rivals\, Cee Cee and Bertie&rsquo\;s oil-and-water friendship
  perseveres over the course of 30 years through even the most tragic trial
 s. With a touching vulnerability\, <em>Beaches</em> exemplifies the triump
 h of the human spirit and the bonds of friendship.</p>
LOCATION:Majestic Theatre\, 245 West 44th St\, New York NY 10036
END:VEVENT
